Program: Outlook
Title: Aljazeera TV and the Prince Claus Fund
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbqzx
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Aljazeera TV and why it has won an award for free speech funded by the Prince Claus Fund. Also - Chef Claudia Roden, another Prince Claus Fund prize winner and how spices can bring countries closer together, a look at Swiss bank accounts and their use by the developing world's dictators, homelessness in New York, living on the Greenwich Meridian in London, and finally, Miriam Makeba performs a click song. Show less